97
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,340
Now,

98
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:38,790
a mirror is a system such that

99
00:04:38,790 --> 00:04:42,240
when an electromagnetic wave falls on it,

100
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,360
a conductor,

101
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,360
an electric conductor,

102
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:47,130
is such that current can flow due

103
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:49,700
to the electric field in any direction,

104
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:53,160
