109
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:03,320
Because they produce currents in there,

110
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:06,500
and those currents produce the reflected wave.

111
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,820
Exactly how that works,

112
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,240
we don't have to worry about here,

113
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:12,860
but it also works in this grid.

