00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:16,370
The only difference is that the electric

115
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:19,680
current can only oscillate in this grid.

116
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,720
In the vertical direction.

117
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:24,300
And so as far as the vertical direction goes,

118
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,780
the grid is a mirror.

119
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:29,520
It reflects waves whose electric field is vertical.

120
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:33,500
As far as the horizontal direction goes,

121
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:35,540
the grid isn't there at all.

122
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,360
It cannot,

123
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,250
the electric wave cannot drive

124
00:05:39,250 --> 00:05:41,140
currents in the horizontal direction,

125
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,830
so it's exactly as if there

126
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,180
was no grid there at all,

127
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:46,280
and the photon just goes straight through.

128
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:49,100
So the result is a grid like this

