00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:46,500
now comes the kicker.

221
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,160
The kicker has to do with symmetry.

222
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:51,130
The symmetry is the symmetry

223
00:09:51,130 --> 00:09:53,680
of rotation of the xy plane.

224
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:57,260
If it's possible to hold your polarizer vertically,

225
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,460
and it's possible to hold it horizontally,

226
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,880
then the symmetry of physics,

227
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,600
which allows you to rotate things,

228
00:10:05,319 --> 00:10:08,209
allows you to construct a

229
00:10:08,209 --> 00:10:11,100
polarizer which points at any angle.

230
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:15,340
What happens to a photon which goes through that?

231
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:21,820
It comes out polarized at an angle.

232
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:23,940
Well,

233
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:26,000
you can imagine classical setups.

234
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:27,500
For example,

235
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,240
a kind of setup which would emit,

