00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:35,440
which was polarized horizontally,

240
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,580
would not go through.

241
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,920
Any kind of device that I

242
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,460
try to think of like that,

243
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:43,830
I tend to find would also

244
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:47,200
block a bullet that was polarized

245
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:51,280
