00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:08,080
it would also block things which were not horizontal.

253
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:11,320
Here's where the kicker is.

254
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:14,660
The kicker is that these

255
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:17,640
non-vertically or non-horizontally polarized photons

256
00:11:18,439 --> 00:11:21,860
may or may not go through this polarizer.

257
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:24,980
They may or may not go through with a probability.

258
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:26,920
What's more,

259
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,640
