261
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:33,980
some piece of it going through,

262
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,540
some piece of it not going through.

263
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:38,060
There are only two possibilities.

264
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,820
And that's it.

265
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,300
It either goes through or it doesn't go through,

266
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:46,180
even though it has been polarized in some other direction.

267
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:49,940
That's where the peculiarities of quantum mechanics start.

268
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,900
That's where you begin to wonder,

269
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:55,100
is the photon really behaving like a particle,

