00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,680
up a theory of the probabilities

274
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:07,080
for the photons to pass through the respective polarizers.

275
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,920
That theory is of course quantum mechanics.

276
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,800
And it is really quite hard

277
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:18,760
to think of a classical setup

278
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:21,220
which would produce the

